IMPORTANT: Before writing the file, read `web/lib/api/types.ts` and `web/lib/api/client.ts` to check:
1. What types are exported (OnboardScan, ScannedDependency, OnboardSelection, etc.)
2. What the `onboard` API client methods look like
3. What fields `OnboardApplyResult` has (NOT `sources_created` ŌĆö check the actual fields)

